verbs.description: President Donald Trump Trump [V: has] repeatedly attacked special counsel Robert Mueller for racking up millions of dollars in expenditures on the Russia investigation . But what Mueller has spent is dwarfed by the amount of taxpayer money Trump has spent on his frequent golfing trips to his Mar - a - Lago resort in Florida .
